1. *Ukus* njegovih kolača je nezaboravan. (The taste of his cakes is unforgettable.)
2. Ona je volela plesati uz *ukuse* narodne muzike. (She liked to dance to the tunes of folk music.)
3. *Ukusna* hrana je neophodna za zdravu ishranu. (Tasty food is necessary for healthy nutrition.)
4. On je imao izuzetan *ukus* za odabir muzike. (He had an exceptional taste for music selection.)
5. Njegovi pokušaji da se prilagodi i da se uklopi u društvo su bili uzaludni, njegov *ukus* nikad nije bio prihvaćen. (His attempts to fit in and conform to society were futile, his taste was never accepted.)